Smaller my ass, Cook, except for maybe your frontal lobes. I will always be here to point out the error of your ways. I am your albatross, your cross to bare, and now that I hear you are a member of the cloth, I am your temptation and your christ to boot.  Tough rough to haul, eh cookie?  I never get smaller, I just admit when I am wrong, and grow wiser and bigger. (except my waist line, damn, wish it would go down to where it was during the 60's-something I suspect we all share too.)<br><br>
Tom, who has been around longer than any of what I &quot;lovingly&quot; call the hyena pack, look around you. Where are the old posters? Where is DocDel? Has anyone heard from him? Is he MIA or even alive?  That is reality, my friends, and while you break wind and each others back, a real man may be gone or dead.  Does that matter to you boys?  Tom, you above all else, who has a well oiled brain, for god sakes stop sucking up to the pack of hyena's who have taken over this site.  Look around you man, who else has joined since they took over?  Wake up Tom, I see a steady decline in your strong moral positions lately, and I think it is because of the company you are trying to gain acceptance from.<br><br>
The &quot;holy&quot; cookie knows the truth, if you lay down with swine, don't complain when you wake up with pigs.  Come on Tom, Help us find out if Doc Del is still with the program, or even alive.
